      "content": "Eugenicists claimed that certain \"races,\" like whites, were superior due to their alleged proximity to the ideal \"Aryan\" type, ascribing desirable traits such as intelligence, morality, and physical beauty to this supposed mystical heritage. They argued that people of African descent and others were \"inferior\" because they were deemed to carry \"undesirable\" genes that threatened the purity and advancement of the white race. Additionally, they used flawed scientific theories like eugenics and anthropology to justify the forced sterilization, segregation, and even mass murder of those deemed \"unfit\" or \"undesirable.\" This distorted logic was meant to maintain and reinforce white supremacy.",
